Subject: [PATCH 17/41] feat(ike_init): separate IKE_INTERMEDIATE rounds for
 5-RTT PQ-GM-IKEv2

Implement proper separation of IKE_INTERMEDIATE exchanges:
- Round 0: Certificates only (no KE) - for SM2 dual cert distribution
- Round 1: SM2-KEM key exchange
- Round 2: ML-KEM key exchange

Key changes:
- Add intermediate_round field to track current IKE_INTERMEDIATE round
- Modify build_i_multi_ke to skip KE in round 0
- Modify process_i_multi_ke to not call key_exchange_done() when no KE
- Modify build_r_multi_ke to skip KE response in round 0
- Modify process_r_multi_ke to detect certificate-only round

This ensures the 5-RTT flow is:
RTT1: IKE_SA_INIT (x25519)
RTT2: IKE_INTERMEDIATE #0 - SM2 dual certificates
RTT3: IKE_INTERMEDIATE #1 - SM2-KEM
RTT4: IKE_INTERMEDIATE #2 - ML-KEM
RTT5: IKE_AUTH
