 =?UTF-8?q?DIATE=20=E5=8F=8C=E5=90=91=E8=AF=81=E4=B9=A6=E4=BA=A4=E6=8D=A2?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=E6=AD=BB=E9=94=81=E9=97=AE=E9=A2=98?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

问题：在 CERT_SEND_IF_ASKED 策略下，发起方等待收到证书才发送，
导致双方都不发送证书（死锁）。

修复：发起方在 IKE_INTERMEDIATE #0 (message_id == 1) 无条件发送证书，
不管证书策略是什么。

结果：
- 发起方报文从 126 字节增加到 1232 字节
- 双向证书交换成功
- IKE_SA 建立成功
---
 src/libcharon/sa/ikev2/tasks/ike_cert_post.c | 14 ++++++++++----
 1 file changed, 10 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/libcharon/sa/ikev2/tasks/ike_cert_post.c b/src/libcharon/sa/ikev2/tasks/ike_cert_post.c
index 629b018fad..fb1f35bcdf 100644
--- a/src/libcharon/sa/ikev2/tasks/ike_cert_post.c
+++ b/src/libcharon/sa/ikev2/tasks/ike_cert_post.c
@@ -730,11 +730,17 @@ METHOD(task_t, build_i, status_t,
 			build_certs(this, message);
 			break;
 		case IKE_INTERMEDIATE:
-			/* PQ-GM-IKEv2: Send dual certificates in first IKE_INTERMEDIATE */
-			if (should_send_intermediate_certs(this, message))
+			/* PQ-GM-IKEv2: Send dual certificates in first IKE_INTERMEDIATE
+			 * IMPORTANT: Initiator MUST send certificates unconditionally in IKE_INTERMEDIATE #0
+			 * regardless of cert policy. This is because:
+			 * 1. Initiator is the first to send in the exchange
+			 * 2. Responder will only reply with certs after receiving initiator's certs
+			 * 3. If initiator waits for certs (CERT_SEND_IF_ASKED), we get a deadlock
+			 */
+			if (message->get_message_id(message) == 1 && !this->intermediate_certs_sent)
 			{
-				DBG1(DBG_IKE, "PQ-GM-IKEv2: building certificates for "
-					 "IKE_INTERMEDIATE exchange");
+				DBG1(DBG_IKE, "PQ-GM-IKEv2: build_i - initiator sending certificates "
+					 "unconditionally in IKE_INTERMEDIATE #0");
 				build_intermediate_certs(this, message);
 			}
 			break;
