Subject: [PATCH 39/41] feat(gmalg): add native HMAC-SM3 integrity algorithm
 implementation

Implement HMAC-SM3-128 (1056) and HMAC-SM3-256 (1057) for IKE/ESP
integrity protection using standard HMAC construction (RFC 2104)
with SM3 hash function from GmSSL library.
---
