Subject: [PATCH 41/41] feat: add SM4, HMAC-SM3 andgorithms forfor IKE/ESP
 proposals

This commit includes:
- gmalg plugin: native HMAC-SM3 signer implementation
- gmalg_plugin.c: updated to use new HMAC-SM3 signers
- hasher.c: updated to support HASH_SM3 and PRF_SM3 in switch
- iv_gen.c: updated to handle SM4 encryption algorithms
- proposal_keywords_static.txt: added sm4/hmacsm3/prfsm3 keywords

Docker configs (initiator/responder):
- swanctl.conf: updated with pqgm-5rtt-gm-symm connection
- Uses SM4-CBC + HMAC-SM3 + x25519 + SM2-KEM + ML-KEM-768
